{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 55,
  "title": "第五十五章（玄符）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "含德之厚，"
    },
    {
      "text": "比於赤子。"
    },
    {
      "text": "毒蟲不螫，"
    },
    {
      "text": "猛獸不據，玃鳥不搏。"
    },
    {
      "text": "骨弱筋柔而握固。"
    },
    {
      "text": "未知牝牡之合而朘作，精之至也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "終日號而不啞，和之至也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "知和日常，"
    },
    {
      "text": "知常日明，"
    },
    {
      "text": "益生日祥，"
    },
    {
      "text": "心使氣日強。"
    },
    {
      "text": "物壯則老，"
    },
    {
      "text": "謂之不道，"
    },
    {
      "text": "不道早已。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂含懷道德之厚也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "神明保佑含德之人，若父母之於赤子也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "蜂蠇蛇虺不螫。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "赤子不害於物，物亦不害之。故太平之世，人無貴賤，仁心，有刺之物，還返其本，有毒之蟲，不傷於人。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "赤子筋骨柔弱而持物堅固，以其意心不移也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "赤子未知男女會合而陰陽作怒者，由精氣多之所致也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "赤子從朝至暮啼號聲不變易者，和氣多之所至也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人能和氣柔弱有益於人者，則為知道之常也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人能知道之常行，則日以明達於玄妙也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "祥，長也。言益生欲自生，日以長大。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "心當專一和柔而神氣實內，故形柔。而反使妄有所為，和氣去於中，故形體日以剛強也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "萬物壯極則枯老也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "枯老則不得道矣。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 13,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不得道者早死。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
